---
title: HelloHero: Pork Schnitzel & Cheesy Tomato Salad with Roast Potatoes & Smokey Capsicum Relish
description: It’s all hands on deck, this recipe is designed to be cooked by grown-ups and kids together! We’re putting a pep in this pork
schnitzel’s step by adding some Nan's seasoning to the golden panko crumb. Serve up with creamy roast baby potatoes to really
make this dish dance and you’ll be bounding to the dinner table in excitement.

